issue.title: Combine custom logger global threadpools

repository.name: onnxruntime
repository.description: ONNX Runtime: cross-platform, high performance ML inferencing and training accelerator

issue.body:
**Description**:

This PR resolves issue https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/4843

Changes are made to the C and C++ APIs to allow C++ users the ability to use both a global threadpool and custom logger.

I'm open to changing any function names to better conform to the API if there are any concerns.
